nComprehensive English synonyms were provided for each entry to capture the full semantic breadth of the Amharic word.\n\n**Protocol 6: THE GRAMMARIAN (Linguistic Tagging)**\nEach entry was assigned one of the seven major Parts of Speech: Noun, Verb, Adjective, Adverb, Pronoun, Preposition, Conjunction. No sub-categories or morphological details were included.\n\n**Protocol 7: THE FILTER (Size Constraint)**\nAll processed words and their roots consisted of at least two characters, adhering to the minimum length requirement. The single-character conjunction 'ና' (split from several words) was discarded as per this protocol.\n\n**Scholarly Guesses:**\n- For 'ከተለዋዋጩ' ('the changeable one'), the root 'ተለዋዋጭ' was tagged as an Adjective, reflecting its primary descriptive function, even though it can be nominalized.\n- 'ትራንስሌተርስ' and 'ኮንፊዩዝድ' were identified as direct English loanwords. Their transliterated forms were maintained as both 'word' and 'root', and their importance score was slightly adjusted to reflect their foreign origin.","input_words":["ቢያሽከረክሩና","ካላስረከብን","ከምንከስር","ከተለዋዋጩ","ለማድርግና","ተራቁተህና","ታገለግላቸዋለህ","ከህዝቦቻቸው","አጠውልጋ","ይሰፋ","ይደረጅና","ሕይወታትን","ሬዴዮኖች","እነዳይጨልም","የቀርባሉ","እየቀቡት","አልሰበሰበውም","ያልተነካኩ","ካሰፈሩዋቸው","ብዝህነቱ","በየስራውና","ተመሱላቸው","ትራንስሌተርስ","የምንቀየር","ያንጠለጠሉበትን","ለማደባለቅና","የበቃኝ","ይቆላው","ኮንፊዩዝድ","ድብዬ"],"batch_number":301,"batch_label":"Words 9001-9030 (Batch 301/667)","model_version":null},{"id":"abef7fe0-25c5-41eb-a1fc-68be8cdf11cf","created_at":"2026-03-04T12:53:25.325163+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_6.txt","batch_index":9150,"words":[{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማስቆጠር","word":"ባስቆጠርንበት","synonyms":["to cause to count","to cause to score","to register","to make count"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መሰግሰግ","word":"ተሰግስጓል","synonyms":["to be crammed","to be packed","to be squeezed in","to be stuffed"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ፎቶግራፍ","word":"ፎቶግራፍ","synonyms":["photograph","picture","image"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":